title: Fulfilling Your Purpose | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Fulfilling Your Purpose | Joel Osteen
description:
You are full of untapped potential, but you have to do your part to tap into it. When you start taking steps toward the desires God placed in your heart, He will take you further than you’ve ever dreamed.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
